text: Dunărea Galați was a Romanian professional football club from Galați, Galați County, south-east Romania. It was founded in 1970. The club was dissolved in 2014. ==References== Category:20th-century establishments in Romania Category:1970 establishments in Europe Category:2014 disestablishments in Europe Category:Romanian football clubs Category:Galați County
